# node_value_string.scn — 活體牙: 節點本體即時值字串 (experience-parity, TiXL parity)
# 承重線:
#   (1) node_draw.drawChild 在每個 NON-primary 輸入 label 右邊畫 effectiveInput 的即時值字串
#       (TiXL MagGraphCanvas.DrawNode.cs:484 CanvasScale>0.4 + ValueUtils.GetValueString:488-502,
#        Float "%.3f"). 改一個 NON-primary 輸入的值 → 本體那行字串重繪成新值 → 畫面像素變.
#   (2) 值字串讀的是 GRAPH effectiveInput(override else def), 不是側表 → 改 override 必反映.
#
# compound_smoke: Root child 5 = TurbulenceForce (Amount[primary,ordinal0] / Frequency / Phase).
#   Frequency 是 NON-primary 輸入 → 本體顯示 "Frequency 1.200" (預設). Amount 是 primary(ordinal0)
#   → 依 TiXL DrawNode.cs:447 本體不顯示其值 (= --selftest-nodeval nodeShowValueAtScale(*,0)==false).
#
# RED→GREEN:
#   - GREEN: 拖 Frequency → override 變 → 本體值字串重繪 → assert_diff 過 + assert_state 確認值動了.
#   - RED 面: 把 assert_diff 改 assert_same 必紅 (畫面確實變了);
#     或在加此特性前 (本體無值字串) 拖 Frequency 只動 Inspector, node 本體不變.
#
# --- 誠實弱點標注 ---
# assert_diff 比的是整張 full.png — Inspector 的 Frequency 欄位也跟著變, 所以 diff「能過」
#   不能單獨機讀證明「node 本體那行字串」變了 (Inspector 像素變也會讓 diff 過).
#   → 本體值字串的「格式 + 顯示規則 (哪些 input 顯示 / 縮放 gating 0.25/0.4 門檻)」的確定性
#     機讀證明在 --selftest-nodeval (formatInputValue + nodeShow{Label,Value}AtScale, RED→GREEN).
#   → 本 scn 的角色: 證明這條值字串是 LIVE 接到 GRAPH 的 (override 動 → 畫面動), 整合測試.

open app/testdata/compound_smoke.swproj

# 選 TurbulenceForce#5 (有 Frequency/Phase NON-primary 值字串的節點) → 開 Inspector
do selectnode 5
wait 0.3
assert_state '.selectedNode == 5'
echo turbulenceforce-5-selected

# 基線: Frequency 還是預設 (無 override 或預設值), 截圖
assert_state '[.lib.symbols[] | select(.id=="Root") | .children[] | select(.id==5) | .overrides.Frequency // 1.2] | length >= 0'
capture full before_freq
echo baseline-captured

# 拖 Frequency 參數 → override 改變 → node 本體 "Frequency x.xxx" 重繪
do drag @param:Frequency +60 +0
wait 0.4

# (2) 鐵線: effectiveInput 確實動了 (override 寫進 GRAPH, 值字串讀的就是這個)
assert_state '[.lib.symbols[] | select(.id=="Root") | .children[] | select(.id==5) | select(.overrides.Frequency != null)] | length == 1'
echo frequency-override-written-to-graph

# (1) 值字串 LIVE: 畫面必變 (本體字串 + Inspector 一起重繪)
capture full after_freq
assert_diff before_freq
echo value-string-live-frame-changed
